@startuml sequence-authentication
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam backgroundColor white

title OAuth2 Authentication Flow — MFA Template

actor "End User" as User
participant "Angular MFE" as MFE
participant "API Gateway" as AG
participant "MFA" as MFA
participant "Identity Provider (IdP)" as IdP

== Login initiation ==

User -> MFE : clicks "Login"
MFE -> AG : GET /auth/login
AG -> MFA : GET /auth/login\n[X-API-Key-Validated: true]
MFA -> MFA : IdPAdapter.buildAuthorizationUrl()\n(state = random UUID)
MFA --> AG : 302 Location: {idp}/auth?response_type=code\n&client_id=...&state=...
AG --> MFE : 302 redirect
MFE --> IdP : GET /auth\n[browser redirect]

== Identity Provider (IdP) authentication ==

IdP -> User : Login form
User --> IdP : credentials
IdP --> MFE : 302 Location: /auth/callback?code=...&state=...

== Authorization Code exchange ==

MFE -> AG : GET /auth/callback?code=...&state=...
AG -> MFA : GET /auth/callback?code=...&state=...\n[X-API-Key-Validated: true]
MFA -> IdP : POST /token\n[grant_type=authorization_code, code=...,\nclient_id, client_secret]
IdP --> MFA : { access_token, expires_in, ... }
MFA -> MFA : AuthenticationApplicationService.authenticate()\nCreate Session(UUID, userToken, TTL)
MFA -> MFA : SessionStoreAdapter.save(session)
MFA --> AG : 302 Location: /\nSet-Cookie: MFESESSION=<sessionId>; HttpOnly; Secure; SameSite=Strict
AG --> MFE : 302 + Set-Cookie forwarded
MFE -> User : logged in
@enduml
